### EventOra — Organiser Dashboard API Test Requests
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

###############################################
# STEP 0 — Login as organiser to get a fresh token
###############################################

### 0. Login as organiser (id=1)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###############################################
# Paste the token from the response above here:
###############################################
@organiserToken = PASTE_ORGANISER_TOKEN_HERE
@adminToken = PASTE_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

###############################################
# TEST 1 — Get organiser dashboard stats
# Expected: 200 OK
# event_totals.pending_approval should reflect whatever's left after
# your earlier Admin Approval API tests (you approved/rejected events
# 1 and 2 already, so only check event_totals adds up sensibly)
# total_registrations: 3 (excludes the 1 cancelled)
# confirmed_registrations: 2
# attendance.checked_in: 1
# attendance.rate_percent: 50.0  (1 checked in / 2 confirmed)
# capacity.total_capacity: 300 (only event id=3 has registrations)
# capacity.use_percent: depends on total capacity across ALL this
#   organiser's events, not just event 3 - check the math matches
#   confirmed_registrations / sum(capacity) across every event
# average_rating: null (feedback table doesn't exist yet)
###############################################
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/organiser
Authorization: Bearer {{organiserToken}}

###############################################
# TEST 2 — Try the organiser dashboard as faculty_admin (wrong role)
# Expected: 403 Forbidden
###############################################
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/organiser
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###############################################
# TEST 3 — Try the organiser dashboard with no token
# Expected: 401 Unauthorized
###############################################
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/organiser
